lol I did not know THAT is what they believed in.  To me there is a fine line between cult and religion.. I guess the point where I start considering something a cult is when they believe their God (or Gods) are physical beigns that live in a definitive place.  To me "God" means something above, and yet all inclusive, of the physical universe.  I would not call any type of phyiscal beign a "God" regardless of what powers it may have.
<br />

<br />
That is just my opinion though.. without looking up the definitions.<br />
